Privacy Policy — Tempo Boxing                                                                              
                                                                                                                        
  Last updated: April 19, 2026                                                                                          
                                                                                                                        
  Introduction                                                                                                          

  Tempo Boxing ("the app") is developed by Hanbin Cheng. This policy explains what the app does — and doesn't do
   — with your data. The short version: everything happens on your iPhone. Nothing you do in the app is ever sent to us 
  or to any third party.                                                                                                
                          
  What We Collect

  Nothing. The app does not collect, transmit, or store any personal information. There are no user accounts, no        
  sign-in, no analytics, no advertising SDKs, no tracking, and no servers we operate. The app makes no network requests
  on its own.                                                                                                           
                          
  Camera Access

  The app uses the iPhone's front camera to detect your hand movements so it can register your punches. Camera frames   
  are processed on your device by Apple's Vision framework. Frames are:
                                                                                                                        
  - Never saved to disk.                                                                                                
  - Never uploaded anywhere.
  - Never shared with us or anyone else.                                                                                
                                                                                                                        
  The live camera feed is shown only on your screen while the app is open, and is discarded the moment each frame is    
  processed.                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                        
  Camera access is requested the first time you enter a playing mode. You can revoke it at any time in Settings →       
  Privacy & Security → Camera → Real Boxing Training.
                                                                                                                        
  Microphone Access       

  The app uses the microphone only in Beat Workout and Beat Workout 2x modes, where it listens to music playing in your 
  environment so it can spawn targets in time with the beat. Audio is processed on your device in real time. Audio
  samples are:                                                                                                          
                          
  - Never saved to disk.
  - Never uploaded anywhere.
  - Never shared with us or anyone else.
  - Processed only for beat detection, never analyzed for speech or other content.
                                                                                                                        
  The microphone is not used in Punching Only mode or Your Own Song mode. Microphone access can be revoked in Settings →
   Privacy & Security → Microphone → Real Boxing Training.                                                              
                                                                                                                        
  Imported Music          

  When you import a song via "Add Your Song", the app copies the file into its own private, sandboxed storage on your   
  device so it can play the track and pre-analyze its beat pattern. Your music files:
                                                                                                                        
  - Stay entirely on your device.
  - Are never uploaded or transmitted.
  - Are deleted when you remove the track from the app's list or uninstall the app.
                                                                                                                        
  The pre-analysis runs locally on your device; no part of the audio or its analysis leaves the phone.                  
                                                                                                                        
  Data Storage & Sharing                                                                                                
                          
  Because we collect no data, we have nothing to store, sell, share, or disclose. The app does not use third-party      
  analytics, crash reporters, advertising networks, or tracking libraries.
                                                                                                                        
  Children's Privacy      

  The app does not collect any information from anyone, including children under 13. The app is suitable for general    
  audiences.
                                                                                                                        
  Changes to This Policy                                                                                                
  
  If the app's data practices ever change (for example, if a future version adds an optional cloud feature), this policy
   will be updated and the "Last updated" date at the top will change. Material changes will be called out within the
  app itself before they take effect.                                                                                   
                          
